data.description:
Welcome! This charming move-in-ready Lake Worth Beach Cottage awaits you!*The property is currently owner-occupied, showings are available by appointment only.* Step into this gorgeous home and experience paradise! The main house has been completely renovated and features 2 bedrooms, 1 bath, and a versatile office/den space. The main house boasts hurricane impact windows and Class A Protection Rating for safety, energy efficiency, and peace of mind. It also has a new roof installed in 2022, ensuring long-term durability. In addition, there is a detached building on the property with its own bathroom. This versatile space offers possibilities such as  hosting guests, a mother-in-law suite, or utilizing it as a workshop with its own parking area and separate entrance located at the back. Location:
Situated in the desirable Downtown Jewell Neighborhood, this home enjoys a prime address in Lake Worth Beach, offering a desirable blend of urban convenience and coastal tranquility. You'll appreciate the close proximity to Downtown Lake Worth, providing easy access to shopping, dining, entertainment, and recreational options.

Investment Potential:
Whether you are looking for a new home, a vacation destination, or an investment property, this listing offers tremendous potential. Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this unique property.

Note: The property includes a termite bond that is valid for one year, providing additional peace of mind. Moreover, this house listing presents an exceptional opportunity for homebuyers looking to enjoy a low interest rate. The existing FHA mortgage may be assumable, providing substantial financial benefits. You can secure a competitive interest rate significantly lower than what is currently available on the market.
Notify us today to schedule a viewing and discover the possibilities that await you at 506 S K Street, Lake Worth Beach.
